metadata.title: Cherkasy Region

description.description: The situation in Cherkasy region remains largely under control thanks to our victorious armed forces and a timely response from the local community. The region is ready to host immigrants. Help them! Food, warm clothes, medicine, anything counts and is able to make a difference.
